The market is expected to expand at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 5.6% from 2025 to 2032.

7. Are plant-based cappuccinos gaining popularity?
Yes, plant-based cappuccinos, made with alternatives like almond or oat milk, are gaining popularity due to the growing health-conscious consumer base.

8. What role do coffee machines play in the cappuccino market?
Advancements in coffee machines have made cappuccino preparation easier and more efficient, driving increased consumer engagement.

9. Which countries are leading the cappuccino consumption trends?
Countries like Italy, the U.S., and the U.K. are major consumers, owing to their strong café cultures and high coffee consumption rates.

10. How does sustainability impact the cappuccino industry?
